# FaithLog environment examples are split by runtime.
#
# Local app execution:
#   .env.local.example
#
# Docker Compose QA/development:
#   .env.docker.example
#
# Cloud Run production contract:
#   .env.prod.example
#
# Never commit real .env, .env.local, .env.docker, .env.prod,
# Supabase credentials, Upstash credentials, JWT secrets, or Firebase keys.
